a place to define reusable template helpers so you don’t repeat the same logic everywhere.

Think of it like functions + constants for Helm template
so you don’t repeat the same YAML again and again.

_helpers.tpl is a place to define reusable template logic that is used by other Helm YAML files.


rolloutSratergy:
  blueGreen:
    enabled: true
    autoPromotionEnabled: true
    autoPromotionSeconds: 30
    scaleDownDelaySeconds: 30

enabled: true
Helm will create a Rollout resource
➡ Helm will NOT create a Deployment

autoPromotionEnabled: true
After new version is ready in preview service
➡ Argo Rollouts will automatically promote it

autoPromotionSeconds: 30
Wait 30 seconds after preview pods are healthy
➡ Then switch traffic to new version

scaleDownDelaySeconds: 30
Old (blue) ReplicaSet is kept alive for 30 seconds
